                     special_linear (by W. Stein)

EXAMPLES:
    sage: G = Sp(4,GF(7))
    sage: G._gap_init_()
    'Sp(4, 7)'
    sage: G
    Symplectic Group of rank 2 over Finite Field of size 7
    sage: G.random()
    [5 5 5 1]
    [0 2 6 3]
    [5 0 1 0]
    [4 6 3 4]
    sage: G.order()
    276595200

